format long
filename = '2335-1_Export_EEG.EDF';
[dat, label, fs, scle, offs, hdr] = read_edf_new(filename);
% dat is the raw data (1 x N) wher N is the number of channels (exported signals)
% label is the text label for each channel
% fs is the sampling frequency for each channel
% scle is a scale value and offs is an offset value
% hdr is the header file (all values are text and can be seen by typing >> char(hdr{1}))
% The data as a 16 bit integer is in dat - it is a cell array so you can access each
% channel with curly brackets like so
ch1 = dat{1};
ch2 = dat{2};
ch3 = dat{3};
% To scale it correctly you need to use the scle and offs parameters
ch1 = (double(ch1).*scle(1))-offs(1);
ch2 = (double(ch2).*scle(1))-offs(1);
ch3 = (double(ch3).*scle(1))-offs(1);
ch3 = ch3*-1;
%Transform the time into seconds
Time = 1:length(ch3);
timesec = Time/fs(3);
timeh = timesec/3600;
%datestr(seconds(timesec),'HH:MM:SS PM')
% Time windows
% Rec start = 11:10, HIstart = 12:13, HIend = 12:47,
duration = 460800;
% Set the HI start and end time
ini_pre = 506880;
ini_HI = 967680;
% Set the timepoints of interest relative to HI
e_HI = ini_HI + 256*60*35;
ini_inf = ini_HI + 256*60*121
ini_inf =
2826240
ini_4 = e_HI + 256*60*60*4;
ini_8 = e_HI + 256*60*60*8;
ini_12 = e_HI + 256*60*60*12;
ini_16 = e_HI + 256*60*60*16;
ini_20 = e_HI + 256*60*60*20;
ini_24 = e_HI + 256*60*60*24;
ini_28 = e_HI + 256*60*60*28;
ini_32 = e_HI + 256*60*60*32;
ini_36 = e_HI + 256*60*60*36;
%Extract ECG voltage for the time ROIs
[ch3pre] = ch3(ini_pre: ini_pre + duration);
[ch3HI] = ch3(ini_HI: ini_HI + duration);
[ch3_inf] = ch3(ini_inf: ini_inf + duration);
[ch3_4h] = ch3(ini_4: ini_4 + duration);
[ch3_8h] = ch3(ini_8: ini_8 + duration);
[ch3_12h] = ch3(ini_12: ini_12 + duration);
[ch3_16h] = ch3(ini_16: ini_16 + duration);
[ch3_20h] = ch3(ini_20: ini_20 + duration);
[ch3_24h] = ch3(ini_24: ini_24 + duration);
[ch3_28h] = ch3(ini_28: ini_28 + duration);
[ch3_32h] = ch3(ini_32: ini_32 + duration);
[ch3_36h] = ch3(ini_36: ini_36 + duration);
%Create time list
timesec = Time/fs(3);
Extract = [1:length(ch3pre)]

%Test
